---
title: Cuban-Style Beef Picadillo with Hearty Rice & Beans
description: Beef picadillo is a slow-simmered stew enjoyed throughout Latin America. We're making a quick version with sweet and savoury additions like raisins, cinnamon and olives to make it extra delicious. Of course, this Cuban dish wouldn't be complete without some good ol' rice & beans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cuban-style-beef-picadillo-5a68a6e4.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/cuban-style-beef-picadillo-da850bbf.pdf
author: HelloFresh
